		(property "Description" "Audio AVDD LDO (LP5907MFX-3.3, ultra-low-noise 10µVrms / 82dB PSRR@1kHz): regenerates a clean 3V3 (AU_3V3) for the ES8311 AVDD off +5V, isolating the codec analog rail from the Wi-Fi/SMPS-noisy +3V3 plane. EN tied to +3V3 so AU_3V3 sequences up after the digital rail. AU_3V3 → FB1 → AVDD; C23 input / C24 output."
			(at 241.3 156.21 0)
